WEBVTT

00:00.030 --> 00:01.225
<i>Previously on "Suits"...</i>

00:01.226 --> 00:03.367
- Robert Zane made you an offer.
- He did.

00:03.368 --> 00:05.067
You begged me
for a second chance.

00:05.664 --> 00:08.631
And now he's using you
to destroy us.

00:08.667 --> 00:10.333
You waltzed in here thinking
this was gonna be

00:10.368 --> 00:12.502
like some prison movie,
but it's not.

00:12.537 --> 00:14.437
It's just prison.
Welcome to Danbury.

00:14.472 --> 00:16.706
- Mike Ross.
- Frank Gallo.

00:16.741 --> 00:20.109
We're being sued for every
case Mike Ross has ever touched.

00:20.145 --> 00:21.945
You won't admit this whole
thing is your fault

00:21.980 --> 00:23.646
in the first place.
My fault?

00:23.682 --> 00:26.316
If I hadn't brought Mike in,
you'd still be here

00:26.351 --> 00:28.618
sniveling around like
a Goddamn junior partner.

00:28.653 --> 00:30.586
Your fiancé,
you want to call her?

00:30.622 --> 00:33.523
Maybe I'll just send
Rachel a text.

00:33.558 --> 00:35.224
We need to move the money
that we have

00:35.260 --> 00:36.392
in every account
by tomorrow.

00:36.428 --> 00:37.493
We don't need to move it.

00:37.529 --> 00:38.628
We can use their buy-ins

00:38.663 --> 00:39.929
to settle
the class-action lawsuits.

00:39.965 --> 00:41.664
All right, let's go.

00:41.700 --> 00:43.132
I'm in the right cell.
I'm in the one you gave me.

00:43.168 --> 00:45.435
Yeah, but this isn't
the one they gave me.

00:45.470 --> 00:47.470
You said you could've turned
on a guy to get out of here,

00:47.505 --> 00:49.906
but you didn't
because you owe him.

00:49.941 --> 00:51.908
Well, I owe that
son of a bitch too.

00:51.943 --> 00:53.977
- You son of a bitch.
- Take it easy, Mike.

00:54.012 --> 00:55.445
And remember,
I know about you.

00:55.480 --> 00:57.113
And I got your
little girlfriend's number

00:57.148 --> 00:59.082
right here.

01:06.490 --> 01:07.989
<i>You keep watching</i>
<i>that clock,</i>

01:08.024 --> 01:10.225
<i>it's gonna be</i>
<i>a long two years.</i>

01:10.260 --> 01:12.527
Believe it or not, I've been
where you are right now.

01:12.562 --> 01:13.828
You've been thinking about
how to get back

01:13.864 --> 01:15.196
at that son of a bitch
all night.

01:15.232 --> 01:16.464
Spit in his oatmeal.

01:16.500 --> 01:18.600
Shit on his pillow.

01:18.635 --> 01:20.935
Whatever it is, my advice
to you is don't do it.

01:20.971 --> 01:22.904
I don't need any advice
from you.

01:22.939 --> 01:24.572
- Excuse me?
- You're the one

01:24.608 --> 01:28.977
that left me alone with that
psychopath in the first place.

01:29.012 --> 01:30.111
Now I get
why you haven't

01:30.146 --> 01:31.579
said a word to me
since last night.

01:31.615 --> 01:32.780
How the hell did you
think I'd react

01:32.816 --> 01:34.249
after something like that?
Hey, listen, man.

01:34.284 --> 01:35.783
I don't have anything
against you,

01:35.819 --> 01:38.486
but I sure as hell
don't have anything for you.

01:38.522 --> 01:40.388
And I'm not gonna cause trouble
with a guy like that

01:40.423 --> 01:42.724
for someone I've never even met,
so if he wants me

01:42.759 --> 01:45.093
to switch for a few hours,
I'm switching.

01:45.128 --> 01:46.995
To hell with
what happens to me, right?

01:47.030 --> 01:49.297
- Hey, I didn't say that.
- No, you just did it.

