02:13.133 --> 02:14.299
Donna, what are you
doing here?

02:14.335 --> 02:16.068
I come bearing gifts.

02:16.104 --> 02:18.771
That's really nice, but you
don't have to come over here

02:18.806 --> 02:20.206
to check on me.
I'm fine.

02:20.241 --> 02:23.375
Says the girl
in her fiancé's shirt.

02:23.411 --> 02:25.010
Look, I know it's cheesy.

02:25.046 --> 02:26.278
Rachel, you wanted to feel him
next to you.

02:26.314 --> 02:27.947
It's not cheesy.

02:27.982 --> 02:29.748
Thanks, Donna.

02:29.784 --> 02:30.850
Well, you do owe me
a thank you,

02:30.885 --> 02:32.084
but it's not for that.

02:32.120 --> 02:33.486
Because in a couple of hours
it's going to be more

02:33.521 --> 02:36.722
than his shirt
wrapped around you.

02:36.757 --> 02:38.858
Are you saying that you got me
on the visitor's list,

02:38.893 --> 02:40.759
because they said
that if I'm not family--

02:40.795 --> 02:42.695
I don't care what they said.
You're his family.

02:42.729 --> 02:45.063
And you're my family, and I
wasn't going to sleep last night

02:45.099 --> 02:48.167
until I got you
on that list.

02:48.202 --> 02:51.704
I-I don't know
what to say.

02:51.739 --> 02:54.373
Say, "Thank you, Donna,"
and get your ass up there.

03:00.781 --> 03:02.781
What you got in your hand
there, tiger?

03:02.817 --> 03:05.451
Dark roast, splash of cream,
no sugar.

03:05.486 --> 03:06.952
And to what do I owe
the honor?

03:06.988 --> 03:08.554
I was thinking this morning
about the day

03:08.589 --> 03:09.788
you picked me
out of the mailroom

03:09.824 --> 03:11.857
and how far we've come.
You know, it's funny.

03:11.892 --> 03:15.094
I was thinking this morning
about how far we've fallen.

03:15.129 --> 03:17.229
Then let's go put
these lawsuits to bed.

03:36.851 --> 03:38.917
Excuse me, Officer?

03:38.953 --> 03:40.753
I know the phones don't open
until 10:00,

03:40.788 --> 03:42.054
but I was wondering
if it's possible for me

03:42.089 --> 03:43.155
to make a phone call?

03:43.190 --> 03:44.390
Get back in line
and eat your breakfast.

03:44.425 --> 03:45.858
Please.
The only reason I'm asking

03:45.893 --> 03:47.092
is 'cause it's an emergency.
I just need a little--

03:47.128 --> 03:49.028
What, are you on fire?

03:49.063 --> 03:50.896
Your leg broken?

03:50.931 --> 03:52.231
'Cause it looks to me
like you're trying to call

03:52.266 --> 03:53.666
someone out there about
something that happened in here.

03:53.701 --> 03:54.833
You don't understand,
all right, my fiancé is--

03:54.869 --> 03:56.535
No, you don't understand.

03:56.570 --> 03:58.037
Unless there's a bomb
headed for us,

03:58.072 --> 04:00.272
nothing that happens out there
has anything to do

04:00.308 --> 04:02.641
with what happens in here.
You got that?

04:02.677 --> 04:05.044
Yeah, got it.

04:11.451 --> 04:14.186
Hey, I left in such
a hurry last night,

04:14.221 --> 04:15.754
didn't get a chance
to say good-bye.

04:15.789 --> 04:17.088
Well, I'll say it now.

04:17.124 --> 04:19.423
Have a nice life.
Leave me alone.

04:19.459 --> 04:20.892
Don't you want to see
a copy of the pictures

04:20.928 --> 04:22.861
your fiancé sent me
last night?

04:25.199 --> 04:27.766
That's bullshit.
She didn't send you anything.

04:27.801 --> 04:29.467
You're right, she didn't.

04:29.503 --> 04:31.136
She sent 'em to you.

04:31.171 --> 04:32.571
I mean, you're the one
who started it all,

04:32.606 --> 04:34.372
telling her how much
you missed her.

04:34.408 --> 04:35.841
How hard do you think it was
for me to get her

04:35.876 --> 04:38.276
to send a sexy picture to you
after that?

04:38.312 --> 04:41.680
I think that kids today
call it a selfie.

04:43.684 --> 04:45.884
There's no way she sent you
a picture like that.

04:45.919 --> 04:48.186
You're right,
it wasn't sexy.

04:48.222 --> 04:50.956
But what I did,
I photoshopped her face

04:50.991 --> 04:52.591
onto a body that is.

04:52.626 --> 04:54.059
I did such a good job,

04:54.094 --> 04:56.595
no one in here
is ever gonna notice.

04:56.630 --> 04:59.130
Yeah.
I made copies.

04:59.166 --> 05:00.799
One for each guy
in the joint.

05:00.834 --> 05:03.768
Usually, a situation like this,
I would charge a fortune.

05:03.804 --> 05:05.704
But today,
I'm feeling so generous

05:05.739 --> 05:07.405
I'm going to give them away
for free.

05:14.915 --> 05:18.216
Get off him, Gallo!

05:18.252 --> 05:20.852
What? I didn't do shit!
He attacked me!

05:20.888 --> 05:21.920
That is bullshit!

05:21.955 --> 05:23.521
I tried to tell you
that's the guy.

05:23.557 --> 05:24.723
I don't care
what you tried to do.

05:24.758 --> 05:26.358
You wanted an emergency,
now you got it.

05:26.393 --> 05:28.627
Get 'em both out of here.
What?

