<i>♪ See the money,</i>
<i>wanna stay for your meal ♪</i>

05:38.237 --> 05:41.538
<i>♪ Get another piece of pie</i>
<i>for your wife ♪</i>

05:41.574 --> 05:44.708
<i>♪ Everybody wanna know</i>
<i>how it feel ♪</i>

05:44.744 --> 05:48.479
<i>♪ Everybody wanna see</i>
<i>what it's like ♪</i>

05:48.514 --> 05:51.382
<i>♪ I'll even eat a bean pie,</i>
<i>I don't mind ♪</i>

05:51.417 --> 05:55.386
<i>♪ Me and Missy is</i>
<i>so busy, busy making money ♪</i>

05:55.421 --> 05:56.854
<i>♪ All right ♪</i>

05:56.889 --> 05:58.226
<i>♪ All step back,</i>
<i>I'm 'bout to dance ♪</i>

